    {
      "id": "1b34750c-f3ba-8033-a06f-fc2a36edbf50",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The personalization of learning activities in computer-supported collaborative learning is something that has garnered the interest of educational researchers. The recommender system uses Artificial Neural Networks and Weighted Sum Model to recommend which collaborative activities a learner should take going forward. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1b34750c-f3ba-8033-a06f-fc2a36edbf50",
        "parent": {
          "type": "page_id",
